description: Hi, we are Stu and Pam Schmidt, owners of I Luv Coffee Minnesoota, MN only full coffee shop/bistro mobile unit.  We pride ourselves on "outstanding Quality."  We have lots of coffee drinks, such as lattes, mochas, brewed, blended coffees, Americanos, espressos, cold press.  We have awesome fruit smoothies.  We have Chai tea, other teas, caramel apple cider, hot chocolate, frozen hot chocolate, berry lemonades, Italian sodas.  We have Croissant and Pannini sandwiches.  We would love to talk with you if we would be available for your event.  Fundraisers, polar plunges, art fairs, swap meets, church events, marathons, parades, and more.  We are flexible!
name: I Luv Coffee Minnesoota!
